---
title: Panko-Topped Sea Bass with Roasted Veggies and Lemony Pesto Drizzle
description: Fresh and hearty, this crispy-topped fish dinner is hearty and fresh at the same time. Roasted broccolini, squash and red onions are the perfect side and a fresh lemony drizzle brings it all together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bar-en-croute-de-panko-efb2cf6c.jpg
